rticle13 internet censorship plan draws more signatures than any petition in human history|first=Cory|last=Doctorow|publisher=Boing Boing|date=2019-03-05|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306011235/https://boingboing.net/2019/03/05/no-filternets-nein.html}}</ref><ref name=EFF2019Feb>{{cite web |last1=Doctorow |first1=Cory |title=The Worst Possible Version of the EU Copyright Directive Has Sparked a German Uprising |url=https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2019/02/worst-possible-version-eu-copyright-directive-has-sparked-german-uprising |website=Electronic Frontier Foundation |access-date=2019-02-24 |language=en |date=2019-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190223233833/https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2019/02/worst-possible-version-eu-copyright-directive-has-sparked-german-uprising |archive-date=2019-02-23 |url-status=live  }}</ref>，后来于2020年5月30日被黑人男子[[乔治·弗洛伊德|乔治·弗洛伊德]]遇害案的联署超越<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.radiotimes.com/news/tv/2020-06-04/george-floyd-memorial-watch-live/ |title= How to watch the George Floyd memorial online and on TV |publisher= Radio Times |author= Thomas Ling |date= 2020-06-04 |access-date= 2020-06-06 |archive-date= 2020-06-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200624010947/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/tv/2020-06-04/george-floyd-memorial-watch-live/ }}</ref>。

