on-dg-statement|title=BBC – BBC Director-General's statement regarding Jeremy Clarkson – Media centre|access-date=2015-03-25|archive-date=2021-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117094733/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/statements/jeremy-clarkson-dg-statement}}</ref>。

